## TASK PROPERTY TEMPLATE

Use this structure when generating the next task property:

- **Context:** WaaS project, last migration, last feature, Docker/Postgres, design system waas-panel.html, i18n en/pt/es, pipeline required, review last implementation first.
- **1. Backend:** Model (apps/api/app/models/CODE.py), Migration (NNN_CODE.py), Schemas (Create/Update/Response), Repository (get_by_id, list, create, update, delete), Router (api/v1/CODE.py), register in main.py.
- **2. Tests:** test_CODE.py — test_list_no_auth 401, test_list_no_module 403, test_create_valid 201, test_create_invalid 422.
- **3. Frontend:** apps/admin/src/app/app/CODE/page.tsx, TenantLayout, loading/empty/error/data states, SVG or lucide-react only (no emojis).
- **4. Sidebar:** Add after previous item; visible when enabledModules.includes('CODE'); icon lucide or inline SVG; i18n nav.CODE.
- **5. tenant-api.ts:** TypeScript types and function signatures.
- **6. i18n:** en.json, pt.json, es.json — all keys in all 3.
- **Pipeline:** lint -> tests -> build -> container (with log read) -> e2e. Report + next task property -> stop.

